*pypy-2.6.0 (04 Jun 2015)

  04 Jun 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.6.0.ebuild:
  Version bump (p.masked).

*pypy-2.5.1 (12 Apr 2015)

  12 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.5.1.ebuild:
  Update for 2.5.1 version bump.

  08 Nov 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -pypy-2.0.2-r1.ebuild,
  -pypy-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Drop old.

  08 Nov 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> pypy-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Restore keywords now that pypy-bin packages are built.

  04 Nov 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> pypy-2.3.1.ebuild,
  pypy-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Add USE=gdbm to match updated PyPy ebuilds.

*pypy-2.4.0 (21 Oct 2014)

  21 Oct 2014; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Add 2.4.0 without keywords to match dev-python/pypy.

*pypy-2.3.1 (12 Jul 2014)

  12 Jul 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.3.1.ebuild,
  -pypy-2.3.ebuild:
  Version bump for pypy{,-bin}-2.3.1.

  16 May 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -pypy-2.0.2.ebuild,
  -pypy-2.0.ebuild:
  Remove old (slotted) version.

*pypy-2.3 (15 May 2014)

  15 May 2014; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.3.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  09 May 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> pypy-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Add USE=tk for tkinter modules. Bug #509794.

*pypy-2.0.2-r1 (30 Mar 2014)

  30 Mar 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.0.2-r1.ebuild,
  pypy-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Backport the :0 slot switch to pypy-2.0.2 since we have binpackages for this
  version.

  12 Mar 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> pypy-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Add the subslot.

*pypy-2.2.1 (12 Mar 2014)

  12 Mar 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Add virtual for the new pypy.

*pypy-2.0.2 (09 Oct 2013)

  09 Oct 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +pypy-2.0.2.ebuild:
  Add virtual version for PyPy 2.0.2.

  05 Sep 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -pypy-1.9.ebuild:
  Remove PyPy 1.9.

  28 Jul 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> pypy-1.9.ebuild,
  pypy-2.0.ebuild:
  Require USE=ssl on old versions of PyPy for compatibility. Drop HOMEPAGE.

*pypy-1.9 (27 Jul 2013)
*pypy-2.0 (27 Jul 2013)

